reviewText: I've only recently discovered how great Ben 10 is. I've enjoyed watching the short seasons of the original Ben 10. Being able to watch the first four volumes of Alien Force, or the entire first season is excellent.

Title: 4 Kid Favorites Cartoon Network Classic Ben 10 Alien Force

reviewText: It's been over a year and a half since this compilation of the first four original volumes came out, and I'm still waiting for another set collecting the next 4 volumes.  :(This is really the only way to buy these series economically. I wish WB had stuck with releasing them in complete season sets. At this rate, I'll be retirement age before seeing complete seasons of BEN 10: ULTIMATE ALIEN.
Title: 4 Kid Favorites Cartoon Network Classic Ben 10 Alien Force

Title: 4 Kid Favorites Cartoon Network Classic Ben 10 Alien Force

reviewText: The "4 Kid Favorites: Ben 10 Alien Force" set is okay, especially if you don't have any of the first four volumes of the hit Cartoon Network series.So yeah, it's basically the first four individual releases compiled together in one big set at a nice price I may add.  Each disc has the same episodes chronicling the adventures of a teenage Ben Tennyson plus special features on the show itself and more.  (To learn a bit more on these individual releases, check my reviews archive on these and more.)So unless you already have these DVDs, you can get this set if you want to.  Maybe consider this collection "Ben 10 Alien Force: The Complete First Season" or something.  Either way, coming soon to Cartoon Network is a new series called "Ben 10 Omniverse".  Surely that will be something worth seeing.
Title: 4 Kid Favorites Cartoon Network Classic Ben 10 Alien Force
